summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements over a portion of Block 20, State Addition No. 4; over portions of Block B, Supplemental Plat of Dumar's Highland Park Addition; and over portions of the southeast one-quarter of Sections 30 and 31, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. in King County, Washington, for sanitary sewer purposes. (S.W. Kenyon St., et al.; Sanitary Sewer).
